        ('14','5','224.91','1','2022-07-03','1.0','31.30','31.30','420.0','<p>Vinil Abba - Waterloo (Picture Vinyl - Edi&ccedil;&atilde;o limitada) - Importado</p><p>Originalmente lan&ccedil;ado em 4 de mar&ccedil;o de 1974 na Su&eacute;cia, Waterloo &eacute; o segundo &aacute;lbum de est&uacute;dio da banda sueca ABBA.</p><p>Repert&oacute;rio do LP:</p><p>Lado A: 1. Waterloo (Swedish Version) 2. Sitting In The Palmtree 3. King Kong Song 4. Hasta Ma&ntilde;ana 5. My Mama Said 6. Dance (While The Music Still Goes On)</p><p>Lado B: 1. Honey, Honey 2. Watch Out 3. What About Livingstone 4. Gonna Sing You My Lovesong 5. Suzy-Hang-Around 6. Waterloo (English Version)</p>'),
        ('15','5','224.91','1','2020-03-24','1.0','31.30','31.30','420.0','<p>Vinil Abba - Arrival (Picture Vinyl - Edi&ccedil;&atilde;o limitada) - Importado</p><p>Lan&ccedil;ado em 11 de outubro de 1976, Arrival &eacute; um &aacute;lbum de est&uacute;dio da banda ABBA.</p><p>Repert&oacute;rio do LP:</p><p>Lado A: 1. When I Kissed The Teacher 2. Dancing Queen 3. My Love, My Life 4. Dum Dum Diddle 5. Knowing Me, Knowing You</p><p>Lado B: 1. Money, Money, Money 2. That&#39;s Me 3. Why Did It Have To Be Me 4. Tiger 5. Arrival</p>'),
        ('16','1','224.91','1','2020-03-24','15.39','22.3','0.99','101.77','<p>CD ABBA - Voyage (CD - Jewel Case replacement) - Importado.</p><p>Voyage &eacute; o primeiro &aacute;lbum de est&uacute;dio do ABBA em 40 anos.</p><p>Repert&oacute;rio:</p><p>1. I Still Have Faith In You</p><p>2. When You Danced With Me</p><p>3. Little Things</p><p>4. Dont Shut Me Down</p><p>5. Just A Notion</p><p>6. I Can Be That Woman</p><p>7. Keep An Eye On Dan</p><p>8. Bumble Bee</p><p>9. No Doubt About It</p><p>10. Ode To Freedom</p>'),
        ('16','5','296.91','1','2020-03-24','1.0','31.30','31.30','420.0','<p>VINIL ABBA - Voyage (Vers&atilde;o Exclusiva | Vinil Verde) - Importado</p><p>Voyage &eacute; o primeiro &aacute;lbum de est&uacute;dio do ABBA em 40 anos.</p><p>Vinil verde Edi&ccedil;&atilde;o Limitada exclusiva. Inclu&iacute; p&ocirc;ster exclusivo e cart&atilde;o postal.</p><p>Faixas:</p><p>1. I Still Have Faith In You</p><p>2. When You Danced With Me</p><p>3. Little Things</p><p>4. Dont Shut Me Down</p><p>5. Just A Notion</p><p>6. I Can Be That Woman</p><p>7. Keep An Eye On Dan</p><p>8. Bumble Bee</p><p>9. No Doubt About It</p><p>10. Ode To Freedom</p>');
